OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrigitte Macron backs      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Funiforms for French schools
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Brigitte Macron, France's first lady,  
OL,6, has said she believes making school    
OL,7, uniforms mandatory could tackle social 
OL,8, inequality among French students.      
OL,10,FShe said students would also save time 
OL,11,Fin getting dressed and money, which    
OL,12,Fwould not be spent on branded clothing.
OL,14,FHer comments come as France's National 
OL,15,FAssembly debates a bill that, if       
OL,16,Fpassed, would make uniforms mandatory  
OL,17,Fin public schools.                     
OL,19,FEducation minister Pap Ndiaye said he  
OL,20,Fwould not support the legislation.     
